{
  "script_id": "series-convergence",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "把无穷多个数一个接一个加起来，结果会是什么？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "有时它稳稳地停在一个有限的数上，我们说级数收敛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "有时它没有尽头地越加越大，我们说级数发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "geometric",
      "line_id": "geo-1",
      "filename": "geometric-geo-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/geometric-geo-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "先看一加二分之一加四分之一，每项都是上一项的一半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "geometric",
      "line_id": "geo-2",
      "filename": "geometric-geo-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/geometric-geo-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "部分和越来越靠近二，却永远不会超过它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "geometric",
      "line_id": "geo-3",
      "filename": "geometric-geo-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/geometric-geo-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "只要公比的绝对值小于一，几何级数就一定收敛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "harmonic",
      "line_id": "har-1",
      "filename": "harmonic-har-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/harmonic-har-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "再看一加二分之一加三分之一，每项虽然趋于零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "harmonic",
      "line_id": "har-2",
      "filename": "harmonic-har-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/harmonic-har-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "可它的部分和会缓慢地、毫无止境地涨向无穷。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "harmonic",
      "line_id": "har-3",
      "filename": "harmonic-har-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/harmonic-har-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "项趋于零，并不保证级数收敛，这是最经典的陷阱。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "ptest",
      "line_id": "pt-1",
      "filename": "ptest-pt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/ptest-pt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.32,
      "size": 37152,
      "text": "把分母换成 n 的平方，级数就收敛，极限恰是 pi 平方除以六。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "ptest",
      "line_id": "pt-2",
      "filename": "ptest-pt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/ptest-pt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "p 级数在 p 大于一时收敛，小于等于一时发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "ptest",
      "line_id": "pt-3",
      "filename": "ptest-pt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/ptest-pt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "比值判别法看相邻两项之比的极限，小于一收敛，大于一发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.47,
      "size": 39456,
      "text": "切换不同级数，看部分和的曲线是趋于渐近线还是一路上扬。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.59,
      "size": 25488,
      "text": "增大项数 N，感受收敛的稳与发散的缓。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "级数是否收敛，取决于部分和序列有没有极限。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "几何级数与 p 大于一的级数收敛，调和级数发散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "series-convergence",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/series-convergence/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "用比值与 p 级数判据看穿无穷和的命运，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
